{"type":"message","id":"68022d8a","parentId":"c9906781","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:57:37.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've created a comprehensive document summarizing the Harness Engineering content from the Feishu Minutes. Let me also update the daily memory file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hbznc7d80vad_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# memory/2026-04-10.md\n\n## 今天发生了什么\n\n- 用户把我的名字更新为\"瞎子\"（更新了 IDENTITY.md）\n- 用户发来飞书妙记链接《Harness工程导论》，要求我学习并创建\n- 通过浏览器读取了妙记内容（需要用户已登录状态），成功解析并创建了学习笔记文档\n\n## 学习内容\n\n完成了《Harness工程导论》（李志琦老师）学习，创建了 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md\n\n核心内容：\n- Harness 工程四层架构：约束层 → 信息层 → 验证层 → 修正层\n- 与提示工程、上下文工程的关系\n- 三个实践案例（Anthropic 实验、产品报价系统、OpenAI Codex CLI）\n- 用四层框架诊断 AI 系统的方法\n\n## 待处理\n\n无\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-04-10.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":853,"output":255,"cacheRead":42555,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43663,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775800649020,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1df83373-1140-4796-9c9b-fa0d95cb8fba"}}
