{"type":"message","id":"508339a7","parentId":"7fb8890d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:57:48.696Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great, the commit was successful. Let me inform the user about the completion.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"学完了，已创建文档 `HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md`。\n\n**核心内容摘要：**\n\n**Harness 工程 = 约束层 + 信息层 + 验证层 + 修正层**\n\n- **约束层**：定边界（角色、格式、安全），过宽过窄都是坑\n- **信息层**：给模型刚好够的上下文，RAG、知识库注入\n- **验证层**：格式/事实/安全/一致性检查，不通过就走修正\n- **修正层**：重试/降级/转人工/反馈闭环，是保底机制不该频繁触发\n\n关键认知：**Demo 到生产，关键不在模型，在 Harness 工程**。课程明天继续讲落地方法。\n\n文档已保存在工作空间，需要的话可以直接查看或继续补充。🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":659,"output":176,"cacheRead":43451,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44286,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775800661131,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b668c140-586e-40b8-843f-92069badfa78"}}
