{"type":"message","id":"41a93cc8","parentId":"acc548fb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:58:11.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The URL format is still not supported. `minutes` is a different type of Feishu document (飞书妙记), not a standard docx. The feishu-fetch-doc skill says it only supports docx URLs. \n\nBut actually, I already successfully read the content using the browser earlier - so I've already done the learning. The document has already been created. I should just let the user know that the learning is already complete since I managed to read it via the browser.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这个 URL 类型（飞书妙记 minutes）不在 API 支持的文档格式范围内，无法通过 API 直接拉取。\n\n不过没关系——我之前已经通过浏览器直接读取了那个妙记页面，完整学完了内容，并创建了学习笔记 `HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md`。\n\n任务已经完成了，不需要重新授权。要不要我把这个笔记发给你，或者你想让我做什么后续操作？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":342,"output":183,"cacheRead":43899,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44424,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775800684048,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5720bc7d-c916-4be0-8eb0-bf7e4bad28fe"}}
